{{!
    @template mod_simplelesson/manual_grade_row
    Moodle table rendering template for selecting essays to mark

   Context variables required for this template:
    * firstname string user/respondent firstname
    * lastname string user/respondent firstname
    * datetaken int unix date/time
    * mark int current student essay grade
    * status string status of the attempt (complete/incomplete)
    * gradelink string of formatted html representing a url


    Example context (json):
    {
      "firstname": "Fred",
      "Lastname": "Flintstone",
      "datetaken": "14567832",
      "mark": "-1",
      "status": "Complete",
      "gradelink": "https://yourmoodle/mod/yourmod/somepage.php?id=1"
    }
}}
<tr class="danger">
  <td>{{firstname}}</td>
  <td>{{lastname}}</td>
  <td>{{#userdate}} {{datetaken}}, %Y-%m-%d %H:%M  {{/userdate}}</td>
  <td>{{mark}}</td>
  <td>{{status}}</td>
  <td>{{{gradelink}}}</td>
</tr>